```
package main

import (
    "fmt"
    "math"
)

func main() {
    res := math.Round(1.6)
    fmt.Println(res)

    res = math.Round(1.5)
    fmt.Println(res)

    res = math.Round(1.4)
    fmt.Println(res)

    res = math.Round(-1.6)
    fmt.Println(res)

    res = math.Round(-1.5)
    fmt.Println(res)

    res = math.Round(-1.4)
    fmt.Println(res)

    res = math.Round(1)
    fmt.Println(res)
}
```
